Summary: Seen on Dishnet work channel 212 (dish earth).
divs: sighting details(i posted this at http:\\www.homesfornh.com\dish-network-tv\blog\watch-our-planet-on-dish-network\comment-page-1\#comment-629) just to let you know, i did catch a ufo on 5\3\09, from 9:58am to 10:33am. what ever it was big. not nearly as big as them moon. i could tell it was moving fast because i know that the dishnet sat is 23000 miles from earth and this object moved from what looked like a realitively close proximity of the sat to past the earth in this time frame. i could get an idea of the size of the object because the curvature of the earth eclipsed it as it went past and behind the earth. it must have been emitting its own light because when it did pass by the earth, it traveled by the dark side, (over the western pacific and asia). i am not expert on this, it may just have been high enough to where it was reflecting light from the sun. i have this recorded on my dvr.
